title: Ep 150: The New Year - Now What?
description: How did the holidays go? Let's recap. Also, the wisdom of Madea. How can Tyler Perry dressed in a woman's costume give so much wisdom? Emails! Relationship advice, career advice and not feeling good enough. So much to get into - Let's get super deep on it, bros!
